 that the states\nbeing tested are indeed entangled.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Jan 2020 02:44:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 21 Mar 2020 07:21:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-19"}
