.6$\\sigma$ respectively, while the two higher mass peaks\nexceed 5$\\sigma$. The observed peaks are consistent with expectations for\nexcited $\\Omega_b^-$ resonances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Jan 2020 14:41:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Feb 2020 19:13:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-04"}
